searchDocs.title: add​
searchDocs.content: </> Framework:add( providers: {Instance }-- A list of providers to add ) → () Adds providers to the framework to be initialized and started. Framework:add({ provider1, provider2 })

searchDocs.title: init​
searchDocs.content: </> Framework:init( config: {Profiling: boolean?}-- Optional configuration ) → () Initializes the framework, initializing and starting all providers in order. Framework:init({ Profiling = true })
